nodes.text: This clone medical officer was stationed on medical station near Ord Cestus during the Clone Wars.

Around 22 BBY, this clone medical officer was stationed at the Ord Cestus medical station in the aftermath of the Second Battle of Geonosis. Padawans Ahsoka Tano and Barriss Offee were tasked in bringing supply ship TB-73 to the station in order to retrieve medical supplies for Mace Windu's forces on Dantooine. A clone named Scythe brought dozens of brain worm eggs into the Pelta-class frigate and infected the crew, taking control of the ship.

This clone was in the operations center of the station alongside Jedi Master Kit Fisto and Nala Se as Tano managed to gain control of this ship and the frigate was safely docked at the center with the aide of interstellar tugs.
